<emphasis id="9FF3EAEDFFFA647CFF20C7F1A043F93A" bold="true" box="[189,325,1751,1777]" pageId="17" pageNumber="28">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AD3836FFFFFA647CFF20C623A2EAF889" blockId="17.[189,1399,1797,1859]" pageId="17" pageNumber="28">
Named in honour of late Dr Alexander Golikov, outstanding Soviet and Russian malacologist who among other works produced a comprehensive revision of 
